MOTION DOCKET

95-795. State ex rel. Ondusko v. Jarvis, Downing & Assoc.

Franklin County, No. 94APD03-320. On motion to strike. Motion denied.

F.E. Sweeney, J., would grant the motion and dismiss the cause.

On alternative motion to motion to strike. Motion granted.

Moyer, C.J., and Cook, J., dissent. F.E. Sweeney, J., would dismiss the cause.
